      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARRA LAD (6) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at The Gardens in a handy 15.87 beating My Wee Lass. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Will go close again if runs up to latest. FUN EFFECTS (1) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only 0.8 lengths from Fabio Zed in second (17.74) at this track. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to her credit. Bold showing expected. TRALEE LUNA (2) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (17.78) at this track in a Grade 5 over 300m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Can measure up. BLANCO FIRE (4) can measure up with the right run.",
